{"tid":1387383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因為廉署查黑警而開心正是今次抗爭會失敗的原因","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:43:16.000Z","uid":56062,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed74bee7f8afbffeb7ec4501d508f729777fccb","tid":1387383,"uid":56062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"你地明唔明而家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">廉署</span>係查黑警有無收黑錢架咋!<br />\n唔係查黑警有無唔專業對無還手之力的示威者濫用暴力呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後查左佢唔係否定緊黑警盲目咁維護暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係利用緊你地對黑警的仇恨黎誤導你地黎<span style=\"color: red;\">分解整個運動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦講得好岩 (<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471226-20190729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471226-20190729.htm&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=c6921a55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471226-20190729.htm&h=2237db9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471226-20190729.htm</a>)<br />\n我地唔應該因為仇恨而見到黑警比人查D無關痛痕的事就好似得到解脫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地應該針對中聯辦,政府及黑警勾結黑幫, 我地要的是徹底調查警隊濫用暴力<br />\n無錯728有44個義士被補係令人髮指,<br />\n但係冷靜D諗, 佢地有槍有砲, <br />\n武力升級無錯可以另佢地每次出勤危險性增加,<br />\n令新人重新考慮仲做唔做黑警,<br />\n但係亦比佢地有藉口用更高的武力,<br />\n而且無論如何,我地起武力層面唔會夠佢地鬥, <br />\n因為佢地分分鐘連殺示威者都可以合法(當然佢地未必會咁,因為產生出的經濟損失可能好大). <br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">盲目運用武力係絕不鼓勵</span>.<br />\n咁樣落去只會有更多義士送頭,終致失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰術我唔識,不過呢個POST好似幾好:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1385989/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1385989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>BY THE WAY, 你知唔知個個星期咁X樣玩法, 會累到呀SIR 駕車都會瞓著, 咁樣好危險架!! :-[:-[\n仲要發夢都夢到你地班XXXXXXX唔知幾時會發一次癲 WTF#kill##kill##kill##kill#\n請勿失驚無神咁對警察濫用暴力 :-[:-[\n同埋唔好成日好似721咁要呀SIR去完中上環又去元朗, 累X死人咩:-[:-[:-[:-[\n</code><br />\n<br />\n利申:和理非"},{"pid":"6bed5b1d0164a9d771e92aca8e99aef3b0096bda","tid":1387383,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d93421b4cea7225aa2f5574151987fd4aeed1b8","tid":1387383,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"775e710b256b88a088c6d1545b6be8fa681cec63","tid":1387383,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>５/６大要求已經冇意義</strong>"},{"pid":"ba5cb8ffe75f475a85a75c12d4164f2421627d65","tid":1387383,"uid":56062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775e710b256b88a088c6d1545b6be8fa681cec63","tid":1387383,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>５/６大要求已經冇意義</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"唔係無意義<br />\n但堅持更重要"},{"pid":"1b7ac19fbd6adb912cb6fd4a05407c82c3194ed4","tid":1387383,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"廉署唔止查黑錢架"},{"pid":"3db18c2296146abf0dafb28258b5f6b5478bf61e","tid":1387383,"uid":56062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7ac19fbd6adb912cb6fd4a05407c82c3194ed4","tid":1387383,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"廉署唔止查黑錢架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"你岩我錯<br />\n不過查完黑警入晒罪喇 <br />\n我地就要開開心心見到警察跟黨姓?<br />\n咁就覺得問題解決晒?<br />\n然後就好似呢篇文所寫的一樣?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383919</a>"}]}